name: Query
extra-info:
SELECT
    SUM(lo_extendedprice * lo_discount) AS REVENUE
FROM lineorder, dates
WHERE
    lo_orderdate = d_datekey
    AND d_weeknuminyear = 6
    AND d_year = 1994
    AND lo_discount BETWEEN 5 AND 7
    AND lo_quantity BETWEEN 26 AND 35;
